### ========== QUERY PARAMETER TESTS ==========

### Test 1: Get all movies (no filters)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies

### Test 2: Filter by year only
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=2010

### Test 3: Filter by director only
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?director=Christopher Nolan

### Test 4: Filter by title only (partial match)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?title=Dark

### Test 5: Combine year and director
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=2010&director=Christopher Nolan

### Test 6: Combine year and director (no results)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=1993&director=Christopher Nolan

### Test 7: Filter by director (different director)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?director=Steven Spielberg

### Test 8: Filter by year (multiple results)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=1993

### Test 9: Combine title and director
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?title=The&director=Christopher Nolan

### Test 10: Filter by minimum year
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?minYear=2010

### Test 11: Filter by maximum year
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?maxYear=2000

### Test 12: Filter by year range (minYear and maxYear)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?minYear=2006&maxYear=2010

### Test 13: Combine all filters
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?director=Christopher Nolan&minYear=2008&maxYear=2014

### Test 14: Case insensitive search (lowercase)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?director=christopher nolan

### Test 15: Partial title match
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?title=inter

### Test 16: No results (non-existent filter)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?director=Quentin Tarantino

### Test 17: Invalid year parameter (should return all movies)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=invalid

### Test 18: Empty query parameter
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?title=

### Test 19: Multiple filters with partial matches
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?title=the&minYear=2005

### Test 20: Director with year range
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?director=Spielberg&year=1993